- set_meta_tags title: t("home.title"), description: t("home.description"), keywords: t("home.keywords")

.row
  .col
  .col-10
    .row
      .col-12.col-md-8.mt-5
        - days = (Date.new(2025,2,1) - Date.today).to_i
        - if days > 0
          %p.text-center.border.border-primary.p-3
            = "<b>#{pluralize(days, "day")}</b>".html_safe
            = "left for early bird"
            = link_to "STEP conference registration", register_path
        = link_to "https://scholar.hw.ac.uk" do
          %img.img-fluid.w-100{src: "/images/2025/scholar_480x100.png", alt: "Scholar website"}
        %p.mt-3
          = succeed(",") do
            = link_to "Scholar", "https://scholar.hw.ac.uk"
          the online learning resource for schools and colleges established in partnership with Heriot Watt University and ADES,
          marks its 25th anniversary this year. Having registered more than a million learners since its creation, Scholar boasts an
          average of 140,000 students and 15,000 teachers and lecturers registered each academic year.
          = succeed(".") do
            = link_to "Newsletter", "/docs/2025/scholar.pdf"
        = link_to "/stepcast#2024-karen-watson" do
          %img.img-fluid.w-100.mt-3{src: "/images/2024/karen_watson_800x800.jpg", alt: "Karen Watson STEPcast"}
        %h2.text-center.mt-4= link_to t("conference.title", year: 2025), conference_2025_path
        = link_to conference_2025_path do
          %img.img-fluid.w-100{src: "/images/2025/flyer_v2_938x700.jpg", alt: "2025 conference flyer"}
      .col-12.col-md-4.mt-5
        = render "facebook"
  .col
